Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:23:01.70,English3,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H90&\fad(300,300)}The fluttering of the birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:07.61,English3,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H90&\fad(300,300)}Pour both abundance and color,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.71,English3,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H90&\fad(300,300)}Unto this white, forsaken land which has lost its music.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.91,English3,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H90&\fad(300,700)}They shall bring prosperity.
